data.title: The History of Rock & Roll
data.meta_description: Find out how to watch The History of Rock & Roll. Stream the latest seasons and episodes, watch trailers, and more for The History of Rock & Roll at TV Guide
data.text:
1995-1995

Documentary, Music

Watchlist

Not even this tasty 10-part take can truly capture rock's history, but it's a real nice try. A bit talky at times, but look who's talking: Bruce Springsteen, Paul McCartney and Little Richard are among those recalling glory days, including the triumphs of the Beatles and Motown; Bob Dylan's groundbreaking exit from folk; Pink Floyd's classic 'Dark Side of the Moon' album; and the ascendance of the electric guitar, courtesy of the sounds of Eric Clapton, Jeff Beck and Jimi Hendrix.
